snippet.title: Amber Heard and Alyssa Milano fuck up astoundingly || #MeToo shows their true colors... AGAIN
snippet.description:
Correction: I fucked up and said Amber nearly cut off Depp's hand, I meant his finger. Sorry.

Amber Heard faces prison time for falsifying evidence against Johhny Depp, and people are calling out Alyssa Milano for the political hack that she is, and it is GLORIOUS! Go rot in prison, Amber. As for Milano, keep destorying your political capital. It's fucking funny to watch your career self destruct because you can't be bothered to not only be consistent, but use logic for more than 5 seconds.


Sources: https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.nationalreview.com/2020/04/alyssa-milano-discovers-due-process/amp/

https://www.google.com/amp/s/pagesix.com/2020/04/07/rose-mcgowan-rips-fraud-alyssa-milano-over-joe-biden-endorsement/amp/

https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ibtimes.com/amber-heard-could-face-3-years-imprisonment-if-found-guilty-faking-evidence-2953787%3famp=1
